A small magical beast appeared in front of Konoha,
but it showed no signs of hostility.

It's still small, and for some reason, it doesn't
seem to have any hostility... I wonder why...

No way, is this the magical beast I gave birth to
and let escape...?!

lovingly... Konoha couldn't help but embrace the
magical beast in her arms.

So you still remember... Even though you're a
magical beast... You're my child after all, so of
course you're cute... Just wait a moment.

Konoha decided to breastfeed the baby magical
beast...
